ObjectStates.LuaScript:
BCBtype= "armyMat"

function onLoad()
    armyPlacer=getObjectFromGUID("8b7aa6")
    Wait.frames(showMenu,3)
end

function showMenu()
    if self.getPosition().x < -40 then
        if armyPlacer ~= nil then
            armyPlacer.call("armyLoaded")
        end
    end
end
